Cloning a Project

You can use clone mechanism to an existing project and replicate the same data to a new project in the Cisco UCS ADI.

To clone a project, perform the following steps:

 1. In the Project(s)/Domain(s) screen, select the project you wish to clone.

 2. Click Clone. The following window appears

Figure 2-3 Information Window

 3. Click OK. The project is cloned.
